Class RandomPalette

java.lang.Object
  colorLib.Palette
      colorLib.RandomPalette

public class RandomPalette
extends Palette

Create a Palette object with random colors. This class extends the Palette class, so all the methods of the Palette class can be accessed from here.

Author:
Jan Vantomme
